<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/888713-after-finishing-the-book-i-am-still">After finishing the book, I am still puzzled about one thing. At the beginning of the story, Elle told Clara that she had always loved her artwork. When did Elle see Clara&#39;s artwork? Did they ever meet before that day?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_888713'><a id="like_count_community_question_888713" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/888713?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">16 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F352921.A_Fatal_Grace">like</a></span>

