<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/896697-marci"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1202748714i/896697._UX100_CR0,25,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/896697-marci">Marci</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    So we’re made to think Agent Yvette was making phone calls to someone with nefarious plans to take down Inspector Gamache but in the last pages it is <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    So we’re made to think Agent Yvette was making phone calls to someone with nefarious plans to take down Inspector Gamache but in the last pages it is revealed that she was calling her father and in fact it is agent Lemieux who is reporting in to Michel Brébouf.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
